sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Repairer
    participant FE as Frontend (React)
    participant API as Backend API (FastAPI)
    participant AUTH as Auth Middleware
    participant EMB as Embedding Service
    participant VDB as Vector DB (Chroma)
    participant AI as LLM Service
    participant RDB as PostgreSQL

    Repairer->>FE: Ask problem in chat
    FE->>API: POST /chat (query)
    API->>AUTH: Validate token and load user scope
    AUTH-->>API: allowed_machines (+ optional plant/line scope)

    API->>EMB: Embed query
    EMB-->>API: Query embedding
    API->>VDB: Search top-k with metadata pre-filter
    VDB-->>API: Authorized chunks + scores

    API->>API: Compute confidence from scores
    alt Low confidence
        API-->>FE: Clarifying question response
        FE-->>Repairer: Ask follow-up details
    else Sufficient confidence
        API->>AI: Generate grounded answer using retrieved context
        AI-->>API: Diagnosis + causes + solutions + citations
        API->>RDB: Save audit trace (query, chunk_ids, response_id)
        API-->>FE: Response with citations and confidence
        FE-->>Repairer: Render solution + references
    end
